  SP 15/11/2002:-

  New to reports:
     MilkWD = Milk Withdrawal Date,
     OtherWD = Other Withdrawal Date,
     Existing Withdrawal Date in Database is to be taken
     as the Meat WithDrawal.

     withdrawal dates in Med. Treatments Report and Vet. Purchases Report.

  SP 15/11/2002.
