  ****************************************************************************
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  SP 19/11/2002:-

  New routine to locate Batch Number and Expiry Date of Drug Used.
  These fields are located by using the DrugPurchID. DrugPurchID is
  set in the Health event when user selects the Batch Number.

